  "title": "Customer Engagement Executive (Entry-Level | Training Provided)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Customer Engagement Executive (Entry-Level | Training Provided)</strong></h3><p>Are you outgoing, friendly, and enjoy connecting with people? This role is perfect for individuals looking to build a career in <strong>customer engagement, brand promotions, and events</strong>. Full training and mentorship are provided — no prior experience required.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong><br />📌 Engage customers during <strong>on-site promotions and brand activations</strong><br />💬 Explain products and services clearly to create a positive customer experience<br />🤝 Build relationships with customers while representing the brand professionally<br />📊 Assist with event coordination and campaign execution<br />📈 Develop <strong>communication, problem-solving, and customer service skills</strong></p><p><strong>What You’ll Get</strong><br />🎓 Comprehensive <strong>training from fundamentals to advanced skills</strong><br />👔 Mentorship from experienced leaders<br />🏢 Hands-on experience with <strong>brand campaigns and customer activations</strong><br />✈️ Travel opportunities and <strong>performance-based, uncapped earnings</strong><br />🚀 Clear career growth into senior roles in <strong>customer engagement or marketing</strong></p><p><strong>Who This Role Is For</strong><br />😊 Outgoing, personable, and confident in interacting with people<br />👍 Motivated, team-oriented, and eager to learn<br />💡 Interested in building skills in <strong>customer service, sales, and brand marketing</strong><br />✅ No experience required — full training provided</p>",
